TextBody:
Hello Zachary,

Let me know if we can schedule a remote session in order to apply the offline patches in order to update the EPP Server to the latest version, including the patch which fixes the vulnerability on the EPP Server.
Also I will give you the download links for the latest EPP Agents for both Windows and MacOS which are addressing this vulnerability.

Best regards,
Emil
